            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Hd1e108">Rubrica 2</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De patientia et impatientia</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>¶ De patientia et impatientia. Rubrica. 2
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e119">
               <lb ed="#V" n="2"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e116">SAlomon in prouerbiis
      <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>capitulo 14.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e125">Impa
        <lb ed="#V" n="4" break="no"/>tiens operabitur stultitiam. Qui pa
        <lb ed="#V" n="5" break="no"/>tiens est multa gubernatur pruden
        <lb ed="#V" n="6" break="no"/>tia. Qui autem impatiens est exaltat stultiti
        <lb ed="#V" n="7" break="no"/>am suam.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e137"> 
        / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e135">16. capitulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e139">Melior est patiens viro
        <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>forti: et qui dominatur animo suo expugna
        <lb ed="#V" n="9" break="no"/>tor est vrbium</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e148"> 
        / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e148">19. capitulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e150">Qui patiens est su
        <lb ed="#V" n="10" break="no"/>stinebit damnum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e156"> 
        / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e158">25. capitulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e158">Patientia linietur
        <lb ed="#V" n="11"/>princeps.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e164"> 
        / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e168">Idem in ecclesiaste capitulo 7.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e166">Melior
        <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>est patiens arrogante.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e172">
               <lb ed="#V" n="13"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e180">Cronica de nugis philosophorum. capitulo 2. scilicet
        <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>de thalete.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e176">Thales miliseus: qui primus sa
        <lb ed="#V" n="15" break="no"/>piens nominatus est secundum quem et septem sa
        <lb ed="#V" n="16" break="no"/>pientes vocati sunt interrogatus qualiter
        <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>quis infortunium facile feret: ait si inimicos
        <lb ed="#V" n="18"/>peiora pati videat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e190"> 
        / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e199">6. capitulo scilicet de biante.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e192">Bias
        <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>primesis dictus vnus de septem sapientibus di
        <lb ed="#V" n="20" break="no"/>cebat fortunatum esse non patientem infortunia.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e200">
               <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e213">Aristoteles polyticorum libro 8. et finali. capitulo 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e204">Iuue
        <lb ed="#V" n="22" break="no"/>nes propter etatem indelectabile nihil suf
        <lb ed="#V" n="23" break="no"/>ferunt volentes.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e213">
               <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e228">Uirgilius eneide. libro 5. prope finem.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e217">Superanda
        <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>omnis fortuna ferendo est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e223">
               <lb ed="#V" n="26"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e240">Tullius rethoricorum artis veteris. libro 2. capitulo 9.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e227">Pati
        <lb ed="#V" n="27" break="no"/>entia est honestatis: aut vlitatis causa rerum
        <lb ed="#V" n="28"/>arduarum ac difficilium voluntaria ac diur
        <lb ed="#V" n="29" break="no"/>na perpensio.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e237">
               <lb ed="#V" n="30"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e256">Ouidius epistolarum. 5. epistola.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e241">Leniter ex me
        <lb ed="#V" n="31" break="no"/>rito quicquid patiare ferendum est.
        <lb ed="#V" n="32"/>Que venit indigne pena dolenda venit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e249">
               <lb ed="#V" n="33"/>
        / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e270">Idem sine titulo. libro i. capitulo i.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="34"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e253">Leue fit quod bene fertur onus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e259">
               <lb ed="#V" n="35"/>
        / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e282">Libro 2. capitulo 3.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="36"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e263">Heu quam quod cupies ponere: ferre graue est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e269">
               <lb ed="#V" n="37"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e294">Quintilianus declamationum. 10 decla
        <lb ed="#V" n="38" break="no"/>matione.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e273">Leuat omnes cruciatus omnem dolorem prae
        <lb ed="#V" n="39" break="no"/>parata mentem composuisse patientia. Nul
        <lb ed="#V" n="40" break="no"/>la pena est nisi inuito. non habemus vllum ni
        <lb ed="#V" n="41" break="no"/>si ab impatientia dolorem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e286"> 
        / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e312">11. declamatione.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="42"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e288">Leuior est dolor qui disponit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e294">
               <lb ed="#V" n="43"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e324">Paulus apostolus: in epistola ad roma
        <lb ed="#V" n="44" break="no"/>nos. capitulo 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e298">Tribulatio patientiam operatur: pa
        <lb ed="#V" n="45" break="no"/>tientia autem probationem.</quote> <!--274.xml-->
        <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e310">
               <lb ed="#V" n="46"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e343">Seneca tragediarum. in troade capitulo 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e314">Quo plu
        <lb ed="#V" n="47" break="no"/>ra possis plura patienter feras.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e320">
               <lb ed="#V" n="48"/>
        / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e355">In medea. capitulo 4.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="49"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e324">Equum atque iniquum regis imperium feras.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e330">
               <lb ed="#V" n="50"/>
        / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e367">Idem epistolarum ad lucillum. libro 2. epistola 6. et finali.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="51"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e334">Multum addit sibi virtus lacessita.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e340">
               <lb ed="#V" n="52"/>
        / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e379">Idem de prouidentia.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e344">Marcet sine aduersa
        <lb ed="#V" n="53" break="no"/>rio virtus: tunc apperet quanta sit quantumcumque pol
        <lb ed="#V" n="54" break="no"/>leat cum quid possit patientia ostendit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e353"> 
        / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e392">Idem de
        <lb ed="#V" n="55"/>consolatione ad paulinum:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e355">Non ferre mala sua
        <lb ed="#V" n="56"/>non est viri.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e363"> 
        / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e405">Idem in prouerbiis: et macrobius
        <lb ed="#V" n="57"/>saturnaliorum. libro 2. capitulo 18. exautior publii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e365">Fe
        <lb ed="#V" n="58" break="no"/>ras non culpes quod mutari non potest. Fu
        <lb ed="#V" n="59" break="no"/>ror fit lesa sepius patientia.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e375">
               <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e422">Lucanus libro 9.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e379">Gaudet patientia duris.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e383">
               <lb ed="#V" n="61"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e432">Cecilius firmianus de beatam vita. libro 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e387">Pati
        <lb ed="#V" n="62" break="no"/>entia est malorum que aut inferuntur: aut ac
        <lb ed="#V" n="63" break="no"/>cidunt cum equanimitate perlatio.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e395">
               <lb ed="#V" n="64"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e446">Prudentius de psicomachia. capitulo 4.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="65"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e399">Omnibus vna comes virtutibus associatur:
        <lb ed="#V" n="66"/>Auxiliumque suum fortis patientia miscet.
        <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>Nulla anceps lucramen init virtute sine ista
        <lb ed="#V" n="68"/>Uirtus: nam vidua est quam non patientia firmat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e411">
               <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e464">Cato. capitulo 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e415">Maxima etenim morum. sem
        <lb ed="#V" n="70" break="no"/>per patientia virtus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e422"> 
        / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e475">Capitulo. 4.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="71"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e424">Quod merito pateris patienter ferre memento.
        <lb ed="#V" n="72"/>Cumque reus tibi sis ipsum te iudice damna.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e432">
               <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>
        / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e489">Capitulo. 5.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="74"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e436">Cede locum lesus: fortune cede potenti.
        <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>Ledere qui potuit: poterit aliquando prodesse.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e444">
               <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e503">Boetius de consolatione. libro 2. capitulo i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e448">Equo
        <lb ed="#V" n="77"/>animo vt toleres oportet: quicquid intra
        <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>fortune aream geritur. In patientia sortem
        <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>exacerbabis quam mutare non possis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e458"> 
        / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e517">7. capitulo.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="80"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e460">Quis ille tam felix qui cum dederit impatien
        <lb ed="#V" n="81" break="no"/>tie manus statum suum mutare non oportet.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e468">
               <lb ed="#V" n="82"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e531">Cassiodorus epistolarum libro 10. epistola 11.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e472">Susti
        <lb ed="#V" n="83" break="no"/>nendo potius quam vindicando laudaberis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e478">
               <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e543">Gregorius in pastorali. capitulo 34.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e482">Tanto mi
        <lb ed="#V" n="85" break="no"/>nus quisque ostenditur doctus quanto mi
        <lb ed="#V" n="86" break="no"/>nus conuincitur patiens.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e491"> 
        / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e556">52. capitulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e493">Quisque non
        <lb ed="#V" n="87"/>tam que ab altero tollerat quam que ab ipso
        <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>tolerantur attendat. si enim sua que portan
        <lb ed="#V" n="89" break="no"/>tur considerat: ea que ab altero sustinet le
        <lb ed="#V" n="90" break="no"/>uius portat.</quote> <!--275.xml-->
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e507">
               <pb ed="#V" n="118-v"/>
               <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
               <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e580">Isydorus solliloquiorum: libro 2. capitulo 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e515">Omnia
        <lb ed="#V" n="2"/>aduersa equo animo porta. Dum tibi aliena
        <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>pericula memoras: mitius tua portas. alio
        <lb ed="#V" n="4" break="no"/>rum enim exempla dolorem releuant. Alie
        <lb ed="#V" n="5" break="no"/>nis malis facilius consolatur homo. Ab vno
        <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>ferendum est: quod multis accidit tolerabile.
        <lb ed="#V" n="7"/>Qui aduersa patientur tolerat: deum sibi ci
        <lb ed="#V" n="8" break="no"/>tius placat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e534"> 
        / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e603">17. capitulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e536">Patienter leuiora porta
        <lb ed="#V" n="9" break="no"/>bis<sic>:: b</sic><!--extra letter?--> grauiora fueris recordatus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e542">
               <lb ed="#V" n="10"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e618">Bernardus de improbatione vitiorum. capitulo 4.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="11"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e546">Nobilis exuperat duras patientia linguas
        <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>Nullius aduersi patiens furore mouetur.
        <lb ed="#V" n="13"/>Et expectata ferunt valiturum semina fructum
        <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>Et sua vir patiens vota videbit ouans.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e556">
        <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e636">Mattheus vindocinensis in poetria parte i.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="16"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e560">Patientia conseruatiua est virtutis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-d1e570">
               <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>
        ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Rd1e648">Ricardus iudex venusinus libro de pertracta
        <lb ed="#V" n="18" break="no"/>tione nuptiarum capitulo 40.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="19"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d92511-Qd1e574">Quam patimur iuste non ita pena riget.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
